\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 Betty: Dad, we cannot work together. Don't you remember the Lemon Ice King disaster? She doesn't listen to me.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 Ignacio: That was a long time ago, and it wasn't her fault.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 Betty: S\hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 he refused to wear a hairnet. That man choked on her bobby pin, and I was the one who got fired. Look, I love her, but it's not a good fit.
