 Nah. And you know how every year Eternal 18 has an exact knockoff of "it," mere days later? Who do you think tips them off for a big\hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0  old bag of cash?
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 Amanda: What?! You've been selling your integrity to some tacky mall store? Genius. Count me in.
