\par }{\insrsid16466024\charrsid14441919 \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 6) }{\insrsid12875027\charrsid14441919 \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 Wilhelmina: Please. There's enough leftover skin from your surgeries to make a bed for my cat.
\par \hich\af0\dbch\af14\loch\f0 Fabia: For your information, this not surgery. This duck sauce.
